  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this retrospective study was to evaluate the incidence of SSI after colorectal
      surgery under the general anesthesia by different general anesthetic technique: inhalation
      versus total intravenous anesthesia.
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
